Package com.nokia.maps.sharing

The sharing package provides classes for sharing a rendered map, location or place.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SharingManager
    This class used to create URLs that can be shared with other users.

Package com.nokia.maps.sharing Description

The sharing package provides classes for sharing a rendered map, location or place. To use this functionality, you need an instance of com.nokia.maps.search.SharingManager, which you can obtain with the method SharingManager.getInstance().
